Expr: A primitive peg/leg grammar to parse arithmetic expressions
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Requirements
============

peg/leg - http://piumarta.com/software/peg
jam - http://public.perforce.com/wiki/Jam

* you can use build.sh script if you don't have jam.

Building
========

$ jam
or
$ ./build.sh

Files
=====

test_expr.sh
------------

Please run the unit test script if anything is added or changed.

expr.leg
--------

The grammar with the C utility functions embedded in the peg/leg grammar.
